### telemetry.py ŌĆö OpenTelemetry tracing
```python
class Telemetry:
    def __init__(self, service_name="ai-orchestrator", otlp_endpoint=None, sample_rate=1.0)
    @property
    def tracer(self)
    def create_span(self, name, attributes=None, parent=None)
    def add_event(self, span, name, attributes=None)
    def record_exception(self, span, exception, attributes=None)
    async def shutdown(self)
```
Use OpenTelemetry SDK. If no endpoint, use in-memory exporter for testing.

