    def set_active_agents(self, count)
    def observe_provider_latency(self, provider, ms)
    def inc_provider_error(self, provider, error_type)
    def set_memory_usage(self, bytes)
    def set_pool_size(self, state, count)
    def get_metrics_text(self) -> str
```
Use prometheus_client.

### logging.py ŌĆö Structured logging
```python
class Logger:
    def __init__(self, service_name="ai-orchestrator", log_level="INFO", json_output=True)
    def bind(self, **kwargs)
    def info(self, msg, **kwargs)
    def warn(self, msg, **kwargs)
    def error(self, msg, **kwargs)
    def debug(self, msg, **kwargs)
    def with_task(self, task_id) -> "Logger"
    def with_agent(self, agent_id) -> "Logger"
```
Use structlog.

